1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:53,880
Meng Wan.

3
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:57,640
You've truly let me down.

4
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:02,240
What are you talking about?

5
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:04,719
I don't understand.

6
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,359
Just now,

7
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:09,359
when Yu Ming presented the
"Spring River" to the Princess Consort,

8
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,640
were you mute?

9
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,799
You saw it too.

10
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:18,400
Lady Cheng'en didn't give me
a chance to speak.

11
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:19,959
Fine.

12
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,000
Then let me ask you this.

13
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:27,640
The manor is heavily guarded.

14
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:31,159
The gown and the box,

15
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:34,840
you were the only one watching them.

16
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,640
So, how come there are rats?

17
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:53,540
=Episode 16=

18
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:55,040
Forgive me, Your Highness.

19
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:57,640
I've always served Lord Cheng'en
at the military camp.

20
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:59,040
I'm not an inner court guard.

21
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,200
I've never seen Lady Cheng'en.

22
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,159
But coincidentally,

23
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:02,040
I have seen Lady Cheng'en's

24
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,640
personal maid, Xiaotao.

25
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:05,400
Since Xiaotao isn't here,

26
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,640
please forgive my presumption.

27
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:10,240
Allow me
to verify Lady Cheng'en's identity.

28
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:14,000
Mr. Xiao, I am fine.

29
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,879
Just give me the letter.

30
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:18,960
My Lady.

31
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:26,159
How is my father?

32
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,560
He is in good health.

33
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:29,000
He often speaks of you,

34
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:31,039
worried you might be wronged.

35
00:02:31,199 --> 00:02:32,319
Tell him

36
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,919
that Wenyue treats me well.

37
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:36,479
He doesn't need to worry.

38
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,800
Yes.

39
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,680
Wenyue,

40
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,919
now that the delivery has arrived,

41
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:44,919
let Mr. Xiao have a rest.

42
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,439
I can't wait to see the new fabrics.

43
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,439
Meng Wan.

44
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,240
A rat chewed the silk.

45
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,240
The pheasant's head was severed.

46
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,000
You're trying to get me killed.

47
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:08,639
You've planned this carefully.

48
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:12,319
Too bad, you can't bring me down.

49
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,159
I've always stayed by your side.

50
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:21,479
You're wrong to suspect me.

51
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,639
Is that so?

52
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:30,159
Then help me one more time.

53
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,360
No matter who did this,

54
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,439
say it was you.

55
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:41,360
You're throwing me away.

56
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,639
Throw you away?

57
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,240
Or your family?

58
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,639
Fly high. Don't look back.

59
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:08,120
Our lives rest on your wings.

60
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,240
The situation is escalating.

61
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,000
The whole city is hunting us.

62
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:17,000
But hiding here forever
won't solve anything.

63
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,240
We've waited so long

64
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,639
to take down Wu Lian.

65
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,439
Hold on a little longer.

66
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,959
Here, have something to eat.

67
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:32,959
Your Highness,

68
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,319
I failed to guard the gown.

69
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:39,120
My master is innocent.

70
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:41,319
Let me bear this punishment.

71
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:44,240
Today, I received a gift
from Cheng'en Manor.

72
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,399
I should be happy.

73
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:48,399
But you two showed
great disrespect.

74
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,519
Your Highness,

75
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,680
I failed to guard it.

76
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,199
But the Flower Festival is near.

77
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,720
You need a gown to wear.

78
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:57,680
Let me redeem myself.

79
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,319
Redeem yourself?

80
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,800
If everyone could redeem themselves,

81
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,399
then my cousin,

82
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,800
the Princess Consort, could be
bullied by commoners.

83
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,680
Your Highness,
the Flower Festival nears.

84
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,800
In this city,

85
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:14,199
no one embroiders better than him.

86
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:19,399
Guards.

87
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:22,240
Take Meng Wan
to the manor's death row.

88
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,279
After the Flower Festival,

89
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:25,600
execute her.

90
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,360
Move.

91
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,000
Wenyue.

92
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,720
Ruoheng.

93
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,759
This is an official matter.

94
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:53,639
Why don't you

95
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,199
take me to see the brocade
you brought?

96
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,959
I met briefly with Mr. Xiao.

97
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,279
He said that meeting Miss Rulan,

98
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,839
he made no mistakes.

99
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,360
But the Princess Consort's nanny
seems suspicious.

100
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:21,639
Miss Rulan going to the manor
alone is already a crime.

101
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,879
And our previous actions

102
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,199
caused too much commotion.

103
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:28,360
The Princess Consort knows the Prince
returns soon.

104
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,920
To please him,

105
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:31,399
even if she knows the truth,

106
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:34,040
she has to accept Miss Rulan
as Lady Cheng'en.

107
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,560
That's like

108
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,079
putting her head on the blade.

109
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,240
She could die at any moment.

110
00:06:56,399 --> 00:07:00,040
The fashionable fabrics from
the capital are so vibrant.

111
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:03,319
Wenyue, you grew up in
the capital.

112
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,560
The noble ladies and matrons,

113
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,519
when have they ever had
a fixed standard?

114
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:10,600
Fashion just chases novelty.

115
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,439
(Chases novelty...)

116
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,920
(If the Prince didn't chase novelty,)

117
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:20,360
(why would I have brought
you to Jinxiu City?)

118
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,500
(A Fine Gift from Cheng'en Manor)

119
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:27,720
Your Highness,

120
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:31,920
this fabric truly has
excellent weave.

121
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:39,639
(A Fine Gift from Cheng'en Manor)
Why is Ruoheng's personal seal on it?

122
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,279
Right.

123
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,040
Your Highness, according to protocol,

124
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:48,199
it should bear the seal
of Cheng'en Manor.

125
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,360
(Oh no.)

126
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,240
(Ruoheng used her personal seal.)

127
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:57,839
Perhaps Lady Cheng'en used her
personal seal for official matters,

128
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,199
not caring for such formalities.

129
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,839
Ruoheng, you were careless.

130
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:06,160
Your personal seal is for private use.

131
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,839
Why use it for official gifts?

132
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:12,839
Wenyue.

133
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,360
Wenyue,

134
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:18,160
I was careless.

135
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,000
Given our bond as cousins,

136
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,839
where is the impropriety?

137
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,399
As for you, merchant,

138
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:28,639
first, you curse my cousin
with a headless pheasant.

139
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,600
She was lenient enough not to pursue it.

140
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,440
Now, you attack me?

141
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,720
You're trying to drive a wedge
between us.

142
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,960
Ruoheng,

143
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,519
Master Wu may not have meant that.

144
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,120
Wenyue,

145
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,240
if he meant well,

146
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,519
why attack me again and again?

147
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,639
I am your cousin.

148
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,360
Of course I look out for you.

149
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,320
The Flower Festival is coming.

150
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:54,200
The Prince returns soon.

151
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,919
And he sows discord.

152
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:58,240
Master Wu,

153
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,720
it's obvious you want me out.

154
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,039
If I leave,

155
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,840
how does that benefit you?

156
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,000
Enough.

157
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,440
It's just a seal.

158
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:10,320
Master Wu, don't make
a big deal of nothing.

159
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,519
Ruoheng,

160
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,799
just prove it to him.

161
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,600
What's the harm?

162
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,879
Wenyue,

163
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:22,000
I'm just angry that a lowly merchant

164
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,360
dares to criticize me.

165
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:24,519
In that case,

166
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:26,720
you should produce you personal seal

167
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,960
to prove its authenticity.

168
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:33,799
I personally wrote the words
on this box's seal.

169
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,399
And my father had a craftsman

170
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:39,039
make this seal just for me.

171
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:42,039
Wenyue, surely you've heard of this.

172
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:47,799
Though I don't have the
seal on me now,

173
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,840
you can compare my handwriting

174
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,159
to the characters on the seal

175
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:55,240
and see if I'm telling the truth.

176
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:35,500
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

177
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:38,740
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

178
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:42,700
♪The past no longer binds♪

179
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:46,900
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

180
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:51,460
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

181
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:55,180
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

182
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:57,540
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

183
00:10:57,540 --> 00:11:01,620
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

184
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:04,220
♪For your faith that never broke♪

185
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:08,540
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

186
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:11,340
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

187
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:15,580
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

188
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:19,260
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

189
00:11:19,380 --> 00:11:22,020
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

190
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:24,620
♪One thought turns into ash♪

191
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:30,940
♪No future left to write♪

192
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:33,820
♪If I never fall♪

193
00:11:33,860 --> 00:11:36,220
♪How could this waiting end♪

194
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,580
♪If I bear no scars♪

195
00:11:37,580 --> 00:11:39,900
♪How could I challenge fate♪

196
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:42,260
♪I knew there was no way back♪

197
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:46,260
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

198
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:48,500
♪For your faith that never broke♪

199
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:52,660
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

200
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:55,540
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

201
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:59,940
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

202
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:03,620
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

203
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:06,220
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

204
00:12:06,220 --> 00:12:08,580
♪One thought turns into ash♪

205
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:14,940
♪No future left to write♪

206
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:18,220
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

207
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,620
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

208
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:25,500
♪If we meet again someday♪

209
00:12:25,940 --> 00:12:31,740
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
